{"tid":408203,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"傳說中嘅陰陽路第20集今年上映","createTime":"2017-09-21T04:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T07:02:39.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"619d8337cf5ebbfbcb400599dde72cb88dfa037a","tid":408203,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"20年前，除了是香港回歸，亦是電影第一集《陰陽路》的誕生之年。當年不少電影都是大製作，屬小本製作的《陰陽路》最初不被看好，但首集上畫大收近600萬，於是續集接續集，前後共拍了19集。<br />\n<br />\n雖然不少人認為《陰陽路》很cult，但絕不誇張地說，《陰陽路》其實是不少香港人的集體回憶。在作品面世20周年紀念，古天樂和邱禮濤牽頭拍攝延續篇《常在你左右》，由張智霖、林家棟、蔡卓妍、羅蘭、佘詩曼、林雪、苑瓊丹等主演。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kHSaXzzXacA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkHSaXzzXacA&d=EFgSP%2BxOnlTz%2BsPMS8n1izCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e50400e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kHSaXzzXacA</a>"},{"pid":"d963e295ec34ed700733160eebebb6858140c6c1","tid":408203,"uid":35112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:47:33.000Z","msg":"冇視帝，同雷宇楊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25656c772687a99ef8432a5805411053e262844","tid":408203,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:34:17.000Z","msg":"冇鬼王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0720658a98e37bb4a4e3178aab7aa48381b7ed6","tid":408203,"uid":78666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"合拍片 = 無鬼"},{"pid":"b6a846a59cdc4dae3bb3acf7bb02494c918fe5e1","tid":408203,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:38:52.000Z","msg":"除咗頭兩套叫見得下人,其他真係爛足咁多年,拍個完結篇啦"},{"pid":"90f429b4fb99e1ce1f7a3db9f1ce9e4066c85bad","tid":408203,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:40:38.000Z","msg":"鬼王都無拍乜陰陽路"},{"pid":"ab8ffced3dad9cb249659eb5a1c49d9f60cc2273","tid":408203,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:45:1